• Best for Power Users: It features Gigabit Ethernet and two USB 3.0 ports, making it ideal for advanced users who want to stream local video files (Plex server) or connect external accessories.

While the SHIELD TV Pro is the "Best NVIDIA device," the Apple TV 4K you just purchased is still considered the overall superior streamer for smoothness and simplicity.

• The Apple TV 4K is ideal for pure, simple, buttery-smooth streaming of services like Gaia TV and Netflix due to its faster main processor (A15 Bionic) and superior frame rate matching.
